title: 共产党 Party Conference
subtitle: The 共产党 chooses their new central committee - will the Wittorf Affair have an influence on their choice?
new-page: true
view-if: kpd_relation >= 50 and wittorf_soviet_union = 1 and year = 1929 and month >= 6 and month <= 8
